data.meta_description: Ballantine Books, 1975. 1st printing, Paperback. 12mo. Fair. Item #76074 ISBN: 0246543150 Spine uncreased with rubbed ends. Hinges creased but secure. Covers marked by patina, mildly rubbed edges leaving several small chipped and creases. Upper corner of front cover chipped. 213p. Toned pages unmarked but slightly curled upwards.
